      "value": "<p>You are skilled at returning pain to those who deliver it. You gain the following benefits: </p>\n<ul>\n<li>When you hit with a melee weapon attack using Strength, you deal additional damage equal to your Strength modifier if that creature dealt damage to you since the start of your last turn.</li>\n<li>When you choose to let an attack that would miss you hit you instead, the creature rolls the damage as normal instead of choosing the maximum.</li></ul>",
